HEADWORD: Photorelief
<hw>Pho`to*re*lief"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A printing
surface in relief, obtained by photographic means and subsequent
manipulations.</def> <rj><au>Knight.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
